com.aspose.cells
Interface ICustomParser

public interface ICustomParser

Allows users to add their custom value parser for parsing string values to other proper cell value object.

Parsed value object from given string. If given string cannot be parsed to proper value object, returns null.

getFormat

public abstract java.lang.String getFormat()
Gets the formatting pattern for last invocation of parseObject(java.lang.String). The formatting pattern should be same with Style.InnerCustom of InvariantCulture to be used for formatting corresponding cell in ms excel.
